the goodbr nice appearancebr long battery lifebr configurable notificationsbr variety of watch faces and appsbr easy setupbr br the badbr costbr br overall the pebble steel is a bit of a luxury item but it performs well and looks nicebr br setup the pebble steel comes with the watch and charging cord however it is up to the user to supply the charger that accepts a usb connection if you are like me you have plenty of these from other devices however if you do not just know that you will need an additional accessory just to get up and running the watch charged in a couple of hours and then it was on to the pairing process i installed the pebble app on my samsung galaxy s5 and it was easy to get connected android is all about notifications and the pebble app lets you control which ones go to the watch on a per app basisbr br watch faces the android pebble app is where you go to get watch faces and apps for the pebble i wanted my pebble to look like a normal watch and i went with the analog watch face that comes from the factory while that may seem boring pebble has a wealth of others to choose from including various bands and tv shows you can choose as subtle or outlandish as you desire and the bottom line is that you have choices there are also composite watch faces that include weather notification counts and other items too however be advised that everything that updates the display has a cost in battery lifebr br apps the pebble store has a number of apps to choose from too while there are many for weather sports email and text responders i chose to keep things simple i have dashboard controls phone toggles here to there gives estimated travel time to saved destinations and trello list management such as shopping lists there are also apps for evernote and wunderlist but i found the trello watch app worked best for shopping listsbr br usage i bought my pebble for a pretty specific purpose i keep my phone on vibrate during working hours at a minimum and i often missed calls or text messages with the pebble i am able to see when i get a call or a text and the information display provides useful information to me on the spot i can see who contacted me along with the contents of text messages i also like that i can dismissignore phone calls from the watch the other notification that i have sent to my pebble is calendar reminders it is handy to see where my next meeting is without having to pull my phone out finally i find it much easier to manage the shopping list without having to constantly unlock my phone as you may have gathered the pebble steel is a pure convenience for me albeit one that does what i want it to quite wellbr br battery life battery life is heavily dependent on usage

i had this suit in my amazon cart and actually found it in a local chain sporting goods store i was able to try in on in sizes 3812 and 4014 i am 5334 165 4034 full bust not band 35534 waist 43534 hips and 63534 torso shoulder through crotch and back to shoulder point so im a difficult fit and tyrs online sizing chart had me in a 34 38 and 40 off the charti wear a 1012 in regular clothing top and bottom and a 36b brabr br anyway personal humiliation and selfloathing aside i could not perceive much of a difference in the two sizes i found both to be tight but not too small with good compression and coverage however i found both to feel short in the torso with a pull at the crotchthe dreaded toe they also felt narrow in the crotch on a thinner person this may not be an issue the cutout in the back is high and will provide plenty of backside coverage up and down side to side is another story the higher cut on the leg coupled with the shorter torso makes wedgies a likelihood for a larger backside the top provided plenty of coverage for me bcup and will cover a larger chest the wider straps may provide more support of a larger chest however this is a swimming suit not a bathing suit you will not have padding cups shelf bra or spot control of tummy butt or back fatbr br i didnt find the fit of this suit comfortable in the length had it fit properly the pattern was not as flattering as the on on the suit i ended up buying httpwwwamazoncomspeedowomensrelaunchflybackswimsuitdpb00obwk5sarefsr_1_37ssportsandfitnessieutf8qid1442942179sr137keywordsspeedoswimsuitwomen size 4014br br seems that ordering a size up if you have a long torso or any curves at all is a good idea for swimming not bathing suits in general if you are looking for a very casual fit for just hanging out at the pool youll likely order up a couple of sizes ultimately you should do the leg work to try on clothing of any sort before ordering online beware that many times clothing sold online is the plungebr br the necklace was prime eligible and arrived in 2 days this is pretty rare for amazon jewelry at this price point i usually find it comes from overseas and takes weeks to get it arrived in a huge lightly padded envelope which offered very little protection and is a waste of materials luckily the necklace was safe and sound sealed in a small plastic baggie with a cute business cardthank you from the seller who is a small california based businessbr br the necklace arrived twisted with a small knot so i fixed that up and noticed instantly how short the chain was i only wear 182134 chains and i knew immediately this was not the 1834 that was promised in the product description i measured it and it came in under 1634 it was almost a choker on me however both the chain and the butterly are lightweight and comfortable the butterfly sits nicely without constantly flipping over and the wings are soft rounded edges so it is comfortable to wear i just switched the pendant out to another chain the chain itself isnt bad basic chain that you find with most costume pendant necklaces the clasp is easy to openclose and is securebr br the butterfly itself is adorable it is not quite as shiny as i saw online which i prefer because it gives it a nicer look the metal it is described as bronze does not bend or misshape and the detail on the butterfly is pretty i am glad that the butterfly isnt tiny it is dainty and perfect for a simple lookbr br it is appx 1434 x 1434 for people like me that dont measure in millimetersbr br for the price the detail of the butterfly and the 2 day prime shipping this was a great buy and i will wear the butterfly often this summer on another chain and on a charm bracelet however minus 2 stars as the chain was 234 shorter than described and a better packaging solution would offer more protection to the item and less waste no loss of stars for packaging i hope seller fixes the description of the chain size to match the actual product

let me tell you about this company they are the best of the best i ordered this bracelet and a set of ear rings from them to wear in our family pictures when i first tried the bracelet on it fit but i wanted it to be a little looser so it could slide up and down my wrist a little bit i decided to write a message to the company to see if i could get an extra clasp or two i wrote the email at 830 on a friday night and got the typical message telling me to allow two business days for a response so i didnt expect to hear back from them until monday at the very earliest i dont know anything about where the company is located or anything but literally less than 10 minutes later i got a lovely response from someone in the company asking for more details clarifying what it is i wanted we exchanged several emails back and forth that night almost like i was texting a friend instead of emailing a company i honestly felt bad for sending them a message so late on a friday night the person i corresponded with was absolutely fantastic first thing that next monday morning they mailed me several clasps free of charge what a great company the jewelry is phenomenal as well the bracelet and the earrings are both a great quality for the price the definitely look more expensive than what i paid for them highly recommend

love this is an all inclusive kit including the storage bag to keep all moving parts together as shown in photos i used this on dirty stinky woven athletic running shoes and an all white casual athletic slip on both had seen better days from photo youll notice the foam cleaner breathed life back into both pairbr br foam is far more manageable to use then any liquid soap ive tried it can be applied like mousse to shoe directly or dispensed onto brush as needed the trick to this working is all in the brush itself the small bristles can penetrate thru a weave or into tight knit fabric it also does well on crevasses or designs in rubber soles make tiny circular motions till shoe is covered in a thin foamy layer it is necessary to add a bit of water to help move the soap and spread it out across entire surface once clean use watered down brush to dilute and dissipate the soap then use hand towel to blot and absorb any residual soap or excess water left over and finally air dry i suggest not using dryer it can alter glue causing permanent damagebr br 4oz kit is perfect size for college kiddos in dorm being all inclusive and of smaller scale this easily tucks into dorm room supplies on the go wipes are best for spot cleaning or traveling its always best to remove a stain asap and these will allow one to do so having a college athlete go is very particular about all her shoescleats this is a must have for her investment of footwear i also ordered the 8oz size to have at home for family use everythings the same with the exception of an 8oz foam cleaner hoping this info can help your decision stay safe

ive got a few different tungsten wedding bands that i rotate through and im glad to have added this one to my collection let me tell you why i love tungsten so muchbr price tungsten is one of the cheapest metals out there and you can easily get a quality ring for around 20 this ring in my opinion is severely overpricedbr hardness tungsten is the second hardest material known to man right behind diamond if you tried to cut it with a steel blade at 2000 degrees f you wouldnt make a scratch and speaking of scratches tungsten rings will never scratch in all the years you have them unless you try to carve at it with a sharp diamondbr shine tungsten has a natural shine to it that makes it perfect for mens jewelry it always keep its mirror finish but isnt so light and bright like silver the cool gun metal gray color of it makes it unique sophisticated and just looks badbr emergencies im a paramedic and ive cut off my fair share of rings working ems and in the emergency room when someone sustains enough trauma to their hand or find their ring can bend dent or jam around their finger which can cause serious damage cutting off a gold titanium silver stainless steel platinum or whatever other metal ring can be a difficult and annoying process for everyone involve worst of all if theres severe swelling and the ring isnt cut off quickly it could mean permanent damage or even loss of a finger while all this sounds terrible the worst injury associated with rings that ive seen is something called degloving google image it degloving is when the ring gets caught or snagged on something is on too tight or is causing the finger to swell and it pulls all your skin and fatty tissue off with it basically your finger is nothing but bone and some muscle afterwards which is disgustingbr enter tungsten none of these injuries are even possible with tungsten for one reason brittleness since tungsten is such a hard metal it will never bend dent or jam around your finger if enough force is applied to actually damage it the ring will simply shatter into a few large pieces causing absolutely no or very minimal damage to your finger and contrary to popular belief tungsten rings can easily be removed in an emergency situation simply tap on it from different angles gently with a hammer by applying these low impacts around the ring it weakens the entire structure and will eventually just break right off ive broken off a tungsten ring in less than 5 minutes before which is much faster than titanium or other hard metalsbr basically tungsten is a great metal and the blue inlay adds some character to it my wifes ring has a blue sapphire in it so its nice we sort of matchbr i received this product at a discount or free for my honest review you can check my profile and i first purchased a pair of the sandals blacksnakeskin 3 4 mos ago and left a glowing review i loved the look fit and most importantly the comfort of this twostrap sandal i give it a 5star rating in those categories but i will never buy this sandal again or recommend it because it has a design or manufacturing flaw it occurred in that first pair as well as the second one which i purchased only last month nov the first pair i used mainly to run errands and the second only for indoors the flaw appeared in both situationsbr imbedded in the rubber sole is a plastic or metal support frame it appears the melted rubber was poured over the frame to bond together after wearing the first sandals for 3 mos a portion of the rubber heel began to wear in a slant typical of that foot with only 14 or less worn down the frame was exposed so it meets the floor when i walk and it causes a clicking or tapping sound it was so annoying that i purchased a 2nd pair corkgold and decided i would only wear it inhouse so the bottom wouldnt get scuffed so quickly here it is only one month later and the same thing has happened the same corner of the rubber sole is barely worn and the imbedded frame is becoming exposed i am again making a clickingtapping sound like a pegleg while walking on tile either the rubber is too soft and wears easily or the manufacturer has not imbedded the frame deep enough into the rubber be forewarned

the filgate leather wallet kit model hsw181w3 has two credit card pocketsslots and a coin bag that snaps closed the entire wallet is a bifold that snaps completely shut this wallet is more appropriate for teens and preteens than it is for adults why is that because we adults simply have more personal items that need to be kept in our wallets not all of my cards can fit inside this filgate wallet which is made of 100 genuine leather a man of fiftyfive has more insurance cards business cards and credit cards than a teenager or young adult in collegebr br one of the credit card pocketsslots the lower one was nearly too small for inserting my cards on the other hand the coin bag was of sufficient size i only need to carry a few quarters dimes and nickels for the soda machine at work once in a while ill get a craving for a soft drink normally i make my own with my sodastream that was a gift from a friend the bifold is large enough for carrying paper money i dont carry that much in my wallet i use credit cards for purchasing most everything even the soda machine at work takes a credit cardbr br however with this filgate wallet the righthand edge of the bifold is not sewn it flaps open wide whenever the wallet is unsnapped money receipts extra cards and anything else stored inside the bifold can fall out and become forever lost i would feel more comfortable about carrying this wallet if the righthand edge of the bifold was sewn overall the filgate leather wallet kit model hsw181ws would make a great christmas or birthday present for a teen or preteen it would make a great 34first wallet34 it is too compact for all of my personal belongings

im a woman that wears an average hat size im always interested in reviewing gaiters the first ones out were quite small clearly designed for an asian market the sizing has gotten better and this is one that i can get behindbr br first let me say that i thought it was a bit tighter around the neck than i personally like but i think that has more to do with the fabric not being as stretchy as others the sewn seams seem a bit scratchier than others ive tried too however once its on the gaiter is quite comfortable it sits loosely around my ears but not so loose that it slips down it will i think work well on a mans face because of the extra room so that definitely is something to consider i get around any fogging of my glasses by just pulling the mask over my nose and sitting my glasses on top i also prefer the bandana style bottom because when the gaiter is pulled down theres less fabric bunched upbr br please be aware that while these may fulfill your areas requirements for wearing masks air passes through them quite easily and i dont feel confident theyll do anything to stop a virus they will however stop dust pollen and bugs i took off one star because of the lack of stretch in the fabric and because of the kinda scratchy seams but i will still be happy to recommend this because of the way it fits it really is unisex and i believe most men would be able to wear it comfortably

i wanted to love these and in some ways i do the parts that fit properly are so soft like a second skin if the whole shoe felt that way id live in them however the fit is all off perhaps because they are trying to make a unisex shoe and honestly that just isnt going to work for most feet men and women on average have different shaped feet our gaits are different as is our center of gravity politics aside when it comes to the biology of feet nature really doesnt care about anyones desire for a unisex world i use to wear skater shoes back in the 90s when it was edgy for girls to do so i loved them but i was also painfully aware they didnt really fit right either and id wear thick socks i still did look pretty cool at 19 in my airwalks just sayin but i dreaded the truck across campus on hot daysbr br with womens feet being more tapered and mens wider overall unless we are talking flip flops or maybe some slides unisex sizing is going to be a fail these shoes were no exception they fit all weird like i had a solid inch past my toes and im always a size 6 the length was basically a 7 the footbed was a little bit too wide but not a whole size too wide i could have lived with it but the rest of the shoe fit like a second skin so sizing down would have made that part too smallbr br i could have lived with the fit issues but the sole makes them unwearable there is an oddity to how the nubs in the sole under just your big toe are much harder than the rest of the nubs on the bottom of the shoe its as if all the other nubs have some give but the ones under your big toe are solid rocks like your toe is sitting on a piece of concrete and the rest of the shoe is padded it feels too weird and unnatural to walk that waybr br i see potential in these shoes but they feel like a prototype and not a finished product
